            <description><![CDATA[来点香辣好吃的新疆拌粉<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>【11.8】约粉 新疆鸡肉拌粉295g*2盒 <br> <br>它这个虽然不是正宗的新疆拌粉但是在拌粉里算是特别好吃的那种了👌米粉是细细的吃起来很Q弹也超会吸料，每一口都特别满足<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>里面的鸡肉也很大块，还可以加个卤蛋火腿肠之类的一起拌着吃是真的香 <img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0ivk6jil9j20j60qfadt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0ivk726ptj20j60p20v9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0ivk7idsij20j60pcwh5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0ivk81cogj20j60qjtca.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0ivk8iblaj20j60p5mzr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0ivk8zd9qj20j60p5gp2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
